---
By: J. Krishnamurti
Source:
  ISBN: 978-1571746931
  Locus:
    Page: 296
  Title: The Essential Mystics, Poets, Saints and Sages
---
Meditation is dangerous
for it destroys everything.
Nothing whatsoever is left,
not even a whisper of desite,
and in this vast, unfathomable emptiness
there is creation
and love.
